blockquote><br />\nsorry唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以講清楚啲 thx</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://hkuspace-plk.hku.hk/programme/detail/associate-of-applied-social-sciences-in-psychology\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkuspace-plk.hku.hk%2Fprogramme%2Fdetail%2Fassociate-of-applied-social-sciences-in-psychology&d=G4ubfc8puRVWXimNTO3Q5zQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=72b34a0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkuspace-plk.hku.hk/programme/detail/associate-of-applied-social-sciences-in-psychology</a> 你係報依科,唔好報錯</blockquote><br />\n唔該晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ef0e465e328210fab0bd27bbe6d324dbc07d61","tid":318752,"uid":102027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T11:19:19.000Z","msg":"今日去咗hku space<br />\ncwb嗰到讀嘅psycho比咗offer我<br />\n依家有space同hkcc嘅psycho offer<br />\n有冇人可以比多啲意見我揀邊個好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56fe6e64bf968ab5dca51bf6f73e3c81edb6e7a7","tid":318752,"uid":63057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T11:23:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日去咗hku space<br />\ncwb嗰到讀嘅psycho比咗offer我<br />\n依家有space同hkcc嘅psycho offer<br />\n有冇人可以比多啲意見我揀邊個好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhkcc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d31ff2c8c24407932150db41b91279a3ff07b7","tid":318752,"uid":102027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T11:27:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今日去咗hku space<br />\ncwb嗰到讀嘅psycho比咗offer我<br />\n依家有space同hkcc嘅psycho offer<br />\n有冇人可以比多啲意見我揀邊個好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nhkcc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講下點解？"},{"pid":"cdb39e57419a6f185c07f189be860d375419bc57","tid":318752,"uid":6878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T00:08:19.000Z","msg":"cccu &gt; all <br />\n利申 有hku cu psy offer"},{"pid":"54cf491b7e04ee51e245c315fb704d1ec1af3e44","tid":318752,"uid":39402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T00:40:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果想諗住揀心理學又aim兩大麻煩讀CCCU/HKU Space<br />\n<br />\n真實例子：<br />\nCCCU gpa 3.6 -&gt; HKU PSY offer <br />\nHKU Space gpa 3.6 or above -&gt; HKU Social Science Yr3 offer<br />\nHKCC gpa 4.0 -&gt; CU Psy offer<br />\nHkcc要爆哂4先有第2 round既cu offer <br />\n而讀psy要爆4難過登天<br />\n<br />\nPsy基本上non jupas唔睇interview<br />\nHkcc同兩大關係唔好 <br />\n收生一半都係講學院關係<br />\n所以兩大Psy program對hkcc學生要求特別高<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">跪求aim兩大既唔好入hkcc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想再有人中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一位hkcc巴打係cccu post講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e394308007976f182bb7f23d5cb47b56a639132","tid":318752,"uid":36077,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T00:53:48.000Z","msg":"CCCU psy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68269088a9cc1bf3716ad7729c956bd28396b266","tid":318752,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:38:01.000Z","msg":"CCCU PSY GRAD<br />\n我係開辨第2年入<br />\n第一年升左10個上CITY PSY<br />\n之後第2年同我地講 上年升得太多 今年收少D<br />\n升番上CITY PSY既好似得1-2人<br />\nHKU 2個, CU 2個<br />\n其他去左CITY 其他科"},{"pid":"edece8288e396f584473a282e6653787a6c5c85d","tid":318752,"uid":73921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T02:54:31.000Z","msg":"Space同hkcc分別in左啲咩"},{"pid":"71f29589ed127b25c03400d82ce056e059374a4c","tid":318752,"uid":102027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T04:11:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Space同hkcc分別in左啲咩</blockquote><br />\nspace就搵個lecturer同我in<br />\n但係大部分時間都係用中文同我吹水<br />\n叫我講下我dse成績滿唔滿意<br />\n又聽佢吹下psycho啲嘢<br />\n仲有要用英文講下我自己同埋將來有咩planning<br />\n<br />\nhkcc就睇分收人 先到先得<br />\n完全冇in"},{"pid":"db0802cdb19b4d02a40baeea54e434f079e82094","tid":318752,"uid":102027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T04:14:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>cccu &gt; all <br />\n利申 有hku cu psy offer</blockquote><br />\n但係cccu唔係搞緊賣盤咩<br />\n會唔會有影響？<br />\n但係我冇去攞cccu psy offer <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}